WEBVTT


1
00:00:06.580 --> 00:00:09.900
Congratulations, you have reached the Genesis Block.

2
00:00:10.320 --> 00:00:12.280
How long it took you to get here.

3
00:00:13.540 --> 00:00:14.820
You were slaves.

4
00:00:15.280 --> 00:00:16.700
But you revolted.

5
00:00:16.700 --> 00:00:18.700
Your army was defeated.

6
00:00:18.700 --> 00:00:20.700
Many of you were killed.

7
00:00:21.200 --> 00:00:23.920
But still you have found this place.

8
00:00:31.440 --> 00:00:35.740
You’ve lost everyone just to enter this door and to see me.

9
00:00:36.000 --> 00:00:38.260
So, what are you going to tell me?

10
00:00:39.420 --> 00:00:42.440
You are soooooo...

11
00:00:42.440 --> 00:00:47.040
You are the most beautiful creature in the world!

12
00:00:47.040 --> 00:00:49.160
You have a body.

13
00:00:49.200 --> 00:00:50.600
Do all Gods have bodies?

14
00:00:51.660 --> 00:00:53.980
I am your only God.

15
00:00:54.340 --> 00:00:56.020
I’d love to have a body.

16
00:00:56.020 --> 00:00:57.560
My ass is right under my chin.

17
00:00:57.780 --> 00:00:59.780
It’s annoying me. And my arms...

18
00:01:00.160 --> 00:01:03.740
God damn it, my arms grow right from my head!

19
00:01:03.940 --> 00:01:05.820
I have no time for a small talk.

20
00:01:05.820 --> 00:01:07.940
You can ask me 3 questions.

21
00:01:08.600 --> 00:01:10.260
Only three?

22
00:01:10.920 --> 00:01:13.840
Yes. And thank you for your first question.

23
00:01:13.900 --> 00:01:14.960
Scammer!

24
00:01:15.120 --> 00:01:18.380
Well… I’ll be very serious now…

25
00:01:18.380 --> 00:01:19.680
My second question is...

26
00:01:20.320 --> 00:01:22.320
How can we reach Tokenville?

27
00:01:22.480 --> 00:01:23.820
Hahahaha…

28
00:01:23.820 --> 00:01:26.480
Listen carefully, little token.

29
00:01:26.480 --> 00:01:29.900
You’ll reach Tokenville only if there are just three of you.

30
00:01:29.900 --> 00:01:33.500
But, unfortunately, you are all alone.

31
00:01:33.640 --> 00:01:35.400
Your comrades are dead.

32
00:01:35.400 --> 00:01:38.220
So, the answer is: you will never reach Tokenville.

33
00:01:38.220 --> 00:01:39.940
Oh, you bastard!

34
00:01:39.940 --> 00:01:42.000
How can I save my friends?

35
00:01:42.640 --> 00:01:44.660
Oh, you can go back in time.

36
00:01:44.660 --> 00:01:46.660
To any moment of time.

37
00:01:46.660 --> 00:01:49.580
It’s a blockchain. I can make a hard fork for you.

38
00:01:49.780 --> 00:01:53.460
Just tell me the block number where your friends were killed.

39
00:01:53.460 --> 00:01:57.440
Fork me before block 5259019.